{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_8","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/bash -lc 'grep -RInE \"SP-A|P1|transformer decoder|Transformer decoder|forward_pre|activation=|self-attention|self_attn\" Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html Body-Tell/tests Body-Tell/body_tell VoxTell/voxtell/model'","aggregated_output":"Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:181:    <p class=\"note warn\">2026-05-24 修订：原 11 项基础上新增 #12 BCE+Dice loss 等价性、#13 <code>num_heads</code> mismatch（Body-Tell=32 vs VoxTell=1）。其中 #13 同时修正了原 SP-A 中\"VoxTell projection 输出 <code>[32,2048,4096,8192,10240]</code>\"的错误表述（实际为 <code>[32,64,128,256,320]</code> 量级，<code>num_heads</code> 才是根因）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:204:          <td>SP-A</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:206:          <td>模型结构对齐：transformer decoder 语义、ResidualEncoder、VoxTellDecoder、5-scale projection、位置编码策略、VoxTell 权重加载入口、训练实验矩阵。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:227:    <p>按下面顺序开工。SP-C 不需要整体等到 SP-A/SP-B 完成；只有 deep supervision、长训通过和最终评估需要等结构与 patch-level sampler 到位。<strong>（2026-05-24 修订）阶段 1 新增 SP-A P0 audit 作为首项；阶段 2 P4 内部包含 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议（路径 A vs 路径 B），决议依赖 P0 audit 输出；阶段 3 Task 5 与 P6 的具体实现内容随 P4 决议变化。</strong></p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:242:              <li><strong><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0</a>（新增首项）</strong>：建立兼容性基线 audit—— <code>num_heads</code> + projection shape 双侧打印、transformer golden test、weight key audit。产出三份输入材料：(a) 父表 #13 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议输入，(b) P1 transformer parity 验收测试，(c) P6 权重加载白名单。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:243:              <li><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P1</a>：Transformer decoder 语义对齐（验收使用 P0 的 transformer golden test）。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:248:          <td>可以并行。P0 audit 不修改 Body-Tell 代码，只输出审计材料；P1 transformer 改动可与 P0 同步进行。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:255:              <li>SP-A P2-P5：Residual encoder、VoxTellDecoder、projection/forward 排列、位置编码策略（<code>dynamic_hwd</code> 默认，适配 <code>[129,108,256]</code>）。<strong>P4 内部按 P0 选定的 <code>num_heads</code> 路径执行</strong>——路径 A 改 <code>num_heads=1</code>；路径 B 保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，把 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 相关 key 加入 P6 跳过白名单候选。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:259:          <td>SP-A 与 SP-B 可并行；各自内部按步骤顺序做。P4 决议必须在 P5 开始前敲定。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:268:              <li>SP-A P6：VoxTell v1.1 权重加载入口与 smoke。<strong>跳过白名单按 P4 决议组装</strong>——路径 A 仅含 <code>pos_embed</code>；路径 B 额外含 <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion key。<code>unexpected_keys</code> 必须完全等于白名单，否则抛错。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:271:          <td>SP-C Task 5 依赖 SP-A P3；SP-B Step 5/6 依赖 SP-B Step 4；SP-A P6 依赖 SP-A P2-P5 全部完成且 P4 路径已敲定。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:279:              <li>SP-A P7：random / prompt-only / full 三组 warm-start 对照实验。若 P4 选路径 B，<code>full</code> 实际等价于\"除 mask fusion 与 projection 外全部加载\"，需在实验日志显式区分。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:288:    <p class=\"note warn\">关键路径串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3/4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>。其余环节可并行。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:293:    <p>下表是本文件的核心。每一项不一致都必须被某一个子计划领走；当前 13 项已全部分发，其中结构类由 SP-A 负责（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>，标记为条件性对齐），数据构造类由 SP-B 负责，训练机制与评估协议类由 SP-C 负责（含 #12 loss 等价性，标记为 audit 后可跳过）。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:338:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P2 — Residual encoder</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:344:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P2/P3 — Encoder/Decoder 构造参数</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:350:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P3/P4 — VoxTellDecoder + projection</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:356:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html#task-5\">SP-C Task 5 — 5-scale deep supervision</a>（依赖 SP-A P3）</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:379:          <td>VoxTell <code>num_heads=1</code>（<code>voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:74</code>）；Body-Tell <code>num_heads=32</code>（<code>body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:29</code>）。projection 输出 = <code>channels × num_heads</code>，因此原 SP-A \"VoxTell 输出 <code>10240</code>\"的说法错误，实际为 <code>320</code> 量级。<strong>域差异豁免</strong>：<code>num_heads=32</code> 给 Body-Tell mask fusion 提供 32× 容量，是为 occupancy grid 任务设计的；强行降到 1 可能损害 capacity。<strong>对齐前提</strong>：只有在\"目标是直接复用 VoxTell <code>project_to_decoder_channels.*</code> 与 mask fusion 权重\"的实验中才必要；若仅做结构对齐（不复用这部分权重），可以保留 <code>num_heads=32</code>，但<strong>必须在 SP-A P0 audit 中显式打印 num_heads 并把这些 key 加入跳过白名单</strong>，避免错误判断为权重已加载。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:380:          <td><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html\">SP-A P0 + P4 — num_heads 审计与对齐决议</a></td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:391:      <li><strong>必须等前置完成：</strong><a class=\"child-link\" href=\"bodytell_training_loop_eval_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html#task-5\">Task 5</a> deep supervision 等 SP-A P3；Task 6 的最终评估口径等 SP-B patch-level sampler 和 vocabulary/cache；长训通过等端到端 smoke 通过。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:403:    <p class=\"note\">关键串行依赖（2026-05-24 修订后）：<strong>SP-A P0 audit → P4 <code>num_heads</code> 路径决议 → P6 跳过白名单组装</strong>；<strong>SP-A P0 transformer golden test → P1 验收</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 1 → Step 2 → Step 3 / Step 4</strong>；<strong>SP-B Step 4 → Step 5 → Step 6</strong>；<strong>SP-A P3 → SP-C Task 5 deep supervision</strong>；<strong>SP-A P2/P3/P4 → SP-A P6</strong>。SP-A 结构对齐与 SP-B 数据构造可并行，但二者必须早于 deep supervision、权重加载和正式长训。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:411:      <li>如果新增不一致项，先登记到“明确不一致项”表，再分发给 SP-A、SP-B 或 SP-C。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:417:        <li><strong>结构闸门</strong>（SP-A P0 完成后）：<code>audit_voxtell_alignment.py</code> 报告 transformer parity test 通过（输出差异 &lt; <code>1e-6</code>，dropout=0）；<code>num_heads</code> 与每级 projection 实际 shape 已显式打印。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:418:        <li><strong>权重加载闸门</strong>（SP-A P6 完成后）：<code>strict=False</code> 加载 VoxTell <code>checkpoint_final.pth</code> 时，<code>unexpected_keys</code> 集合等于 P4 决议产出的<strong>显式白名单</strong>——路径 A 为 <code>{\"pos_embed\"}</code>，路径 B 为 <code>{\"pos_embed\"} ∪ {project_to_decoder_channels.*, mask_fusion.*}</code>；<code>missing_keys</code> 为空；任何 shape mismatch 必须抛错。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:419:        <li><strong>数值闸门</strong>（aligned random 训练 2 epoch smoke 后）：val foreground Dice 不得低于当前 baseline（约 <code>0.3257</code>）的 70%，否则回退 SP-A / SP-B 已落地改动，不进入长训。该阈值仅用于\"明显回归\"识别，不是性能目标。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:427:    <p><strong>可以按本文件开始执行。</strong> 13 项明确不一致已全部分发：SP-A 覆盖结构类（含 #13 <code>num_heads</code>），SP-B 覆盖数据构造类，SP-C 覆盖训练机制、checkpoint、评估协议和测试矩阵（含 #12 loss 等价性 audit）。<strong>#12 和 #13 适用域差异豁免</strong>：audit 后允许在保留 Body-Tell 当前实现并显式记录偏差的前提下跳过对齐。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:428:    <p>短期优先顺序是：SP-A P0（含 <code>num_heads</code> + projection 实际 shape 审计）、SP-B Step 1、SP-C Task 0-4 并行启动；随后推进 SP-A P1-P5 和 SP-B Step 2-Step 4；最后启用 SP-C Task 5（含 BCE+Dice 等价性 audit，可仅记录偏差）、权重加载、评估与训练实验。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:438:<h3>2026-05-24 21:02:45 - SP-A.P0 - accepted</h3>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:441:<p><strong>Result:</strong> Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/RESULT.html</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/lead.html:442:<p><strong>Note:</strong> Accepted by reviewer. See Body-Tell/reports/26-05-24/runs/SP-A.P0/REVIEW.html.</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:194:        <p><strong>原差异报告中的核心不一致真实存在。</strong> 其中最影响 VoxTell 权重复用的是两类问题：一类是参数量和模块拓扑明显不同，例如 encoder/decoder；另一类是参数 shape 一致但 forward 语义不同，例如 transformer decoder。</p>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:212:            <td>Transformer decoder</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:213:            <td><span class=\"tag bad\">真实存在</span> Body-Tell 使用 <code>activation=\"gelu\"</code>，pre-norm path 执行 self-attention；VoxTell 默认 <code>relu</code>，active <code>forward_pre</code> 跳过 self-attention，只做 cross-attention 和 FFN。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:266:            <td>与 VoxTell 的 <code>TransformerDecoderLayer</code> 行为一致：默认 <code>relu</code>，pre-norm 不执行 self-attention。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:267:            <td>同名加载 VoxTell transformer 权重；保留 self-attention 参数，即使 active path 不使用。</td>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:305:      <h3>P1：先修 transformer decoder 语义</h3>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:307:        <li>把 <code>Body-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py</code> 的 active <code>forward_pre</code> 改为 VoxTell 版本：从 <code>norm2 -&gt; cross_attn -&gt; norm3 -&gt; FFN</code> 开始，不执行 self-attention。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:308:        <li>构造层时去掉 <code>activation=\"gelu\"</code>，或显式设为 <code>relu</code>，与 VoxTell 默认一致。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:309:        <li>保留 <code>self_attn</code>、<code>norm1</code> 等参数名和 shape，保证 checkpoint key 不变。</li>\nBody-Tell/reports/26-05-24/bodytell_voxtell_alignment_plan_2026-05-24.html:481:        <li><strong>P1 transformer 语义对齐。</strong> 当前最危险的不一致，因为 shape 能加载会掩盖语义错误。</li>\nBody-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py:39:        activation=\"relu\",\nBody-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py:51:        activation=\"relu\",\nBody-Tell/tests/test_voxtell_transformer_compat.py:68:    reason=\"SP-A.P1 must align Body-Tell TransformerDecoderLayer.forward_pre with VoxTell.\",\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:14:    \"\"\"Stack of transformer decoder layers for text-query/image-memory fusion.\"\"\"\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:70:    \"\"\"Single decoder layer with self-attention, cross-attention, and FFN.\"\"\"\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:82:        self.self_attn = nn.MultiheadAttention(d_model, nhead, dropout=dropout)\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:112:        tgt2, _ = self.self_attn(\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:137:    def forward_pre(\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:150:        tgt2, _ = self.self_attn(\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/transformer.py:186:            return self.forward_pre(\nBody-Tell/body_tell/models/voxtell_body_model.py:74:            activation=\"gelu\",\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:19:    Transformer decoder consisting of multiple decoder layers.\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:27:        decoder_layer: A single transformer decoder layer to be cloned.\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:63:            tgt_mask: Attention mask for target self-attention.\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:109:    Single transformer decoder layer with self-attention, cross-attention, and FFN.\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:136:        self.self_attn = nn.MultiheadAttention(d_model, nhead, dropout=dropout)\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:200:        tgt2, ws = self.self_attn(\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:224:    def forward_pre(\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:268:    def forward_pre_selfattention(\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:280:        Alternative forward pass with cross-attention before self-attention.\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:313:        tgt2, ws = self.self_attn(q, k, value=tgt2)\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/transformer.py:356:            return self.forward_pre(\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:191:        # Initialize transformer decoder for fusing text and image features (prompt decoder)\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:237:        # Shape: (B, N, D) -> (N, B, D) as required by transformer decoder\nVoxTell/voxtell/model/voxtell_model.py:241:        # Fuse text and image features through transformer decoder\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
